<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A9404008001">
<title>
Scan Tool Data Definitions
</title>
<topic id = "AENBP70A9404008002">
<title>
Headlight Switch (ON/OFF): 
</title>
<ptxt>
This indicates state of lighting switch.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
ON: Lighting switch is in “ON” position and headlights are on.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
OFF: Lighting switch is in clearance light, “OFF” position and headlights are off.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENBP70A9404008003">
<title>
Windshield Washer Switch (ON/OFF): 
</title>
<ptxt>
This indicates state of windshield washer pump.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
ON: Windshield washer pump is operated.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
OFF: Windshield washer pump is off.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENBP70A9404008004">
<title>
Headlight Cleaner Switch (ON/OFF): 
</title>
<ptxt>
This indicates state of headlight washer switch.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
ON: Headlight washer switch pushed.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
OFF: Headlight washer switch released.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</topic>
</servinfosub>
